<style>
  /* ── GrowDirect — How It Works ── */
    :root {
      --green:#0A4A2F; --accent:#F28C38; --accent-hover:#E07B2D;
      --text:#1A3C34; --text-secondary:#5C6B66; --text-muted:#8A9A94;
      --border:#E8F0EB; --bg:#F8F9FA; --white:#fff;
      --radius:1rem; --radius-xl:1.5rem;
      --font-heading:"Plus Jakarta Sans",-apple-system,sans-serif;
      --font-body:"Inter",-apple-system,sans-serif;
    }
    *,::before,::after { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
    body { font-family:var(--font-body); color:var(--text); background:var(--bg); -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; }
    .container { max-width:880px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 1.5rem; }

    .breadcrumb-bar { background:#fff; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
    .breadcrumb-bar .container { max-width:1100px; }
    .breadcrumb { padding:.6rem 0; font-size:.78rem; color:var(--text-muted); font-family:var(--font-heading); }
    .breadcrumb a { color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:none; }
    .breadcrumb a:hover { color:var(--text); }
    .breadcrumb span { margin:0 .4rem; }

    .page-layout { padding:1.75rem 0 5rem; }
    .section-card { background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:var(--radius-xl); overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
    .section-body { padding:2rem 1.75rem; }

    .page-eyebrow { font-size:.68rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:.4rem; font-family:var(--font-heading); display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:.4rem; }
    .page-title { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:1.85rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); line-height:1.1; margin-bottom:.6rem; }
    .page-intro { font-size:1rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
    .eyebrow-dot { width:5px; height:5px; background:var(--accent); border-radius:50%; animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.4} }

    /* STEP LIST */
    .steps { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
    .step { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:1.25rem; padding:1.25rem 1.5rem; background:var(--bg); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:var(--radius); }
    .step-icon { width:48px; height:48px; min-width:48px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--green); color:#fff; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; }
    .step-icon svg { stroke:#fff; }
    .step-content { flex:1; }
    .step-num { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:.65rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:.2rem; }
    .step-title { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:1rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:.3rem; }
    .step-desc { font-size:.875rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.6; }

    .support-image { width:100%; border-radius:var(--radius); display:block; margin:1.5rem 0 0; }

    .page-layout-single { padding:1.75rem 0 5rem; }
    .page-note { font-size:.9rem; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.65; font-style:italic; margin-top:.5rem; }
    .section-body h2 { font-family:var(--font-heading); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--text); margin:1.5rem 0 .6rem; }
    .section-body h2:first-child { margin-top:0; }
    .section-body p { font-size:.95rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:1rem; }
    .section-body p:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
    .section-body ul, .section-body ol { padding-left:1.25rem; margin-bottom:1rem; color:var(--text-secondary); line-height:1.75; font-size:.95rem; }
    .section-body li { margin-bottom:.5rem; }
    .section-body li:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
    .section-body strong { color:var(--text); font-weight:700; }

    @media(max-width:560px) {
      .step { gap:1rem; padding:1rem 1.125rem; }
      .step-icon { width:40px; height:40px; min-width:40px; }
    }
  </style>

  <div class="breadcrumb-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a><span>›</span>
        <span style="color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">How It Works</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="page-layout-single">
    <div class="section-card">
      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="page-eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-dot"></span> How It Works</div>
        <h1 class="page-title">How It Works</h1>
        <div class="page-intro">A simpler way to shop for your weekly food essentials</div>
        <div class="page-note">GrowDirect is designed to make everyday food shopping more straightforward. Start with a Saver Box that suits your household, add extra produce or pantry staples if needed, and get it delivered across Melbourne metro — with no subscription and no unnecessary complexity.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-card" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <div class="section-body">
        <h2>How GrowDirect Works</h2>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Check your delivery area</strong> — We currently deliver across Melbourne metro. Before you shop, check that your suburb is within our delivery zone.</li>
          <li><strong>Start with a Saver Box</strong> — The easiest way to shop GrowDirect is to begin with a Saver Box. Each box is designed to suit different household sizes and weekly budgets.</li>
          <li><strong>Add extra items if needed</strong> — Once you have chosen your box, you can top up with additional produce, pantry staples, or Weekly Specials.</li>
          <li><strong>Place your order</strong> — Add your selected items to cart and complete checkout online.</li>
          <li><strong>Get it delivered</strong> — Order by the stated cut-off time and we will prepare your order for delivery across Melbourne metro, direct to your door.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Why GrowDirect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Start with the essentials</strong> — Saver Boxes give you a simple foundation for your weekly shop.</li>
          <li><strong>Top up only what you need</strong> — Add extra produce, pantry staples, or Weekly Specials depending on what your household needs.</li>
          <li><strong>No subscription required</strong> — Order when it suits you. GrowDirect is designed for flexibility, not lock-in.</li>
          <li><strong>Built for practical value</strong> — Our range is shaped around real household buying habits, combining convenience with everyday value.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What You Can Shop</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Saver Boxes</strong> — Pre-packed options designed around different household sizes and value needs.</li>
          <li><strong>Weekly Specials</strong> — Seasonal opportunities and value-led offers available for a limited time.</li>
          <li><strong>Mix & Match Essentials</strong> — Extra produce and pantry staples to round out your order.</li>
          <li><strong>Everyday Staples</strong> — Food essentials chosen to make weekly shopping more practical and convenient.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Common Questions</h2>
        <p><strong>Do I need a subscription?</strong><br>No. GrowDirect is designed so you can order when needed, without being locked into a subscription.</p>
        <p><strong>How do I start an order?</strong><br>The easiest way is to begin with a Saver Box, then add extra items such as produce, pantry staples, or Weekly Specials if needed.</p>
        <p><strong>Where do you deliver?</strong><br>GrowDirect currently focuses on Melbourne metro delivery areas. Customers should check suburb availability before ordering.</p>
        <p><strong>Can I add extra items to my box?</strong><br>Yes. After choosing a Saver Box, you can top up with additional items to suit your household.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

